collectionMetadata.name: Healthcare Professional to Population Ratio
collectionMetadata.description:
Notes:

* Doctors: Includes doctors registered under Temporary Registration for service provision from Year 2010 onwards. 
* Nurses: Refers to Registered Nurses, Enrolled Nurses and Registered Midwives. 
* Dentists: Refers to Division I and II dentists. 

The Dentists Register has two divisions. Graduate dentists are listed in the First Division. Dentists without formal qualifications (grand-parented as dentists in the 1950s) and former dental therapists are listed in the Second Division.
